<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title">Ruby on Rails</h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents"><p class="para">Ruby on Rails 是一个用于开发以数据库为后台的 web 应用程序的开源 web 框架。其为发挥程序员持久的生产力而优化，因为它能让程序员通过有益的约定而不是配置来编写代码。</p></div>
<div class="links sectionlinks" role="navigation"><ul>
<li class="links"><a class="xref" href="ruby-on-rails.html.zh-CN#ruby-on-rails-installation" title="安装">安装</a></li>
<li class="links"><a class="xref" href="ruby-on-rails.html.zh-CN#ruby-on-rails-configuration" title="配置">配置</a></li>
<li class="links"><a class="xref" href="ruby-on-rails.html.zh-CN#ruby-on-rails-references" title="参考资料">参考资料</a></li>
</ul></div>
<div class="sect2 sect" id="ruby-on-rails-installation"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title">安装</h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="para">在安装<span class="app application">Rails</span> 之前你应该安装<span class="app application">Apache</span> 和 <span class="app application">MySQL</span>。关于<span class="app application">Apache</span> 软件包的安装， 请参考<a class="xref" href="httpd.html.zh-CN" title="HTTPD - Apache2 Web 服务器">HTTPD - Apache2 Web 服务器</a>。关于 <span class="app application">MySQL</span>则请参考 <a class="xref" href="mysql.html.zh-CN" title="MySQL">MySQL</a>。</p>
<p class="para">当你安装好了<span class="app application">Apache</span>和<span class="app application">MySQL</span>，你就可以安装<span class="app application">Ruby on Rails</span>软件包了。</p>
<p class="para">要安装<span class="app application">Ruby</span>基础包和<span class="app application">Ruby on Rails</span>，你可以在终端输入如下命令：</p>
<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">sudo apt install rails</span>
</pre></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
<div class="sect2 sect" id="ruby-on-rails-configuration"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title">配置</h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<p class="para">
    	Modify the <span class="file filename">/etc/apache2/sites-available/000-default.conf</span>
	configuration file to setup your domains.
    </p>
<p class="para">首先改变的是<span class="em emphasis">DocumentRoot</span>指令：</p>
<div class="code"><pre class="contents ">DocumentRoot /path/to/rails/application/public
</pre></div>
<p class="para">下一步，改变 &lt;Directory "/path/to/rails/application/public"&gt; 指令：</p>
<div class="code"><pre class="contents ">&lt;Directory "/path/to/rails/application/public"&gt;
        Options Indexes FollowSymLinks MultiViews ExecCGI
        AllowOverride All
        Order allow,deny
        allow from all
        AddHandler cgi-script .cgi
&lt;/Directory&gt;
</pre></div>
<p class="para">你也必须为Apache打开<span class="app application">mod_rewrite</span>模块。请在终端输入如下命令来打开<span class="app application">mod_rewrite</span>模块:</p>
<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">sudo a2enmod rewrite</span>
</pre></div>
<p class="para">最后，您将需要改变<span class="file filename">/path/to/rails/application/public</span> 与 <span class="file filename">/path/to/rails/application/tmp</span> 目录的所有权到运行<span class="app application">Apache</span> 进程的用户：</p>
<div class="screen"><pre class="contents "><span class="cmd command">sudo chown -R www-data:www-data /path/to/rails/application/public</span>
<span class="cmd command">sudo chown -R www-data:www-data /path/to/rails/application/tmp</span>
</pre></div>
<p class="para">搞定！现在您的服务器已经可以运行 <span class="app application">Ruby on Rails</span> 应用程序。</p>
</div></div>
</div></div>
